“Some may call them Yoruba Demons but we call them Merry Men.” Sexy Steel has released the video for his new song Merry Men. The song is the official soundtrack for AY Makun’s forthcoming film, Merry Men: Yoruba Demons. The film will be out in cinemas nationwide on 28 September 2018. Read More: Nigerians React To EFCC “Freezing” Davido’s Account Merry Men was produced by Sosick and mixed and mastered by Vc Perez. The official video was directed by Toka McBaror. You can watch the video below: 